description: An innovative, bold lipstick that provides long-wearing, show-stopping color and endless creamy comfort.

Ulta's Lipstick gives full, rich color in a long-lasting formula. Shea butter and hyaluronic filling spheres penetrate lips and provide moisturization and fills in lip lines and wrinkles for a soft and smooth pout. Gluten-free.
Maybelline's Color Sensational The Loaded Bolds Lip Color delivers one-stroke intensity with hyper-color pigments and an opaque, creamy clay base.
A highly-pigmented matte lip color that provides non-drying comfort on the lips and leaves a suede finish.
Creamy, conditioning and ultra-smooth – with hydra-boosting MOISTURE-WRAP™ technology – they glide easily onto your lips and stay firmly in place as you go a-pout your day.

Go PRO with LORAC PRO Matte Lip Color! This velvety-smooth, matte lip color is infused with anti-aging antioxidants of acai berry, pomegranate, grape seed extract and vitamins C and E to help nourish and protect your lips. The PRO tip hugs the curves of your lips with precision and control while the weightless, PRO formula easily glides on with a long-lasting, matte finish. PRO Matte Lip Color comes in an array of highly-pigmented, buildable, rich colors from natural nudes to vibrant hues for a modern, matte lip in any shade you desire. Color, line and define, just like a PRO!
A limited-edition Rouge Pur Couture lipstick, dressed for the holidays, with gold and silver sparkles and a bullet embossed with stars.
NYX Matte Lipstick is a highly pigmented lipstick that glides on smoothly and stays put.
An oil-in-a-stick, medium-coverage lipstick with an innovative texture that provides high-performance color and irreverent shine while it conditions the lips.

Matte lipstick isn't meant to be drying or complicated to wear. Infused with grape seed extract imported from Italy, Milani Matte Color Statement Lipstick dresses up lips with rich, eye-catching color and a suede-like finish while offering the same comfort your favorite cream lipsticks provide. This long-wearing, non-drying matte lipstick takes you from velvety pale pink to voluptuous red—and everywhere in between—with just one stroke.
Formulated to shade, define and showcase the lips. Hundreds of hues, high-fashion textures. The iconic product that made M·A·C famous.

A brilliant formula that pushes the boundaries of colour. Each Lipstick holds intense amounts of pigment, resulting in extreme colour intensity, clarity and vibrancy. This luxurious gelled base melts on contact, providing fully saturated colour with a satin finish in one stroke.
The perfect blend of high fashion colour and comfortable texture. Rich formula glides on with ease, creating perfect coverage and shine.

M•A•C Huggable Lipcolour is back by popular demand. A comforting, creamy formula in shades that stay luminous for up to six hours. This lasting lipstick with rich, glossy shine boosts collagen, leaving lips looking smooth, supple, sculpted. The unique gel base melts upon contact, allowing each shade to glide on effortlessly with a feather-light moisturizing finish.

A 77-Mineral Moist Complex that instantly nourishes lips with maximum moisture in a lightweight, non-sticky formula. Larger bullet applies bright, long-lasting colour in a single stroke. Medium-shine finish, buildable coverage. Magnetic closure.
An innovative lipstick that coats lips with bold color, long-lasting wear, and luxe comfort.

Cremesheen Lipstick, infused with pearlized pigments and a moisturizing serum blend, is available in 10 new Asia-inspired shades. Prominent pinks, radiant reds and contemporary corals flatter all skin tones with a finish that leaves lips luminous. With foolproof colour coverage, this update to Cremesheen is the new yin and yang for your lips.

Experience fuller and more voluptuous lips with a stroke of captivating colour. Butter London's creamy, long wearing formula instantly accentuates lip curves and provides essential moisture. In irresistible shades specially formulated with a Phyto-Endorphin Complex to give you a blissful rush of happy, you'll crave the indulgence.
A collection of high-impact lipsticks in dimensional shades that have been handcrafted to deliver extreme moisture, soft texture, and creamy wear.

It’s time to put your lipsticks on notice. Milani Amore Matte Lip Crème has arrived. This revolutionary, highly saturated liquid-to-matte formula dries to a soft, velvety finish for fuller-looking lips. Its double-sided, flexible plush applicator hugs the contours of lips, working to lock in bold, opaque color. Non-sticky, smooth and ready for all-night wear (up to 16 hours!), our Amore Matte Lip Crème is the ultimate transfer resistant kiss-me-matte.
High-definition color meets velvety matte with Revlon Ultra HD Matte Lipcolor. With a unique gel formula and a lightweight, moisturizing feel. For love that draws you in – in 8 shades.

Pure Red- Neither lipstick nor lip gloss, this matte lip cream is a new kind of lip color that goes on silky smooth and sets to a matte finish. Soft Matte Lip Cream is surprisingly durable and unlike some matte lipstick formulas also moisturizing.

Give your lips a colorful makeover with the Revlon ColorStay Ultimate liquid lipstick. This lipstick is food proof and doesnt fade after meals. It's formulated with an ultra-conditioning topcoat, so you dont have to wear a separate topcoat. One-step application. Available in assorted shades.

Designed for styles ranging from modern minimalist to bold and dramatic, this high-definition, saturated formula starts as a traditional lipstick that's been liquefied and concentrated, resulting in a luxurious, moussey texture with a sophisticated, matte finish. It comes in an array of on-trend bold and everyday shades and features a Tarteist Paint Brush Wand with an ergonomically slanted, soft applicator so anyone can paint on precise pigment no matter your Tarteist skill level.
Go beyond gloss with Maybelline's LipStudio Color Jolt Intense Lip Paint - glides on to deliver a jolt of intense color.
Maybelline's Color Sensational Vivid Matte Liquid Lip Color has a creamy liquid base for a soft, cushiony feel.

L'Oréal's Infallible Pro-Matte Gloss is their first high-impact matte gloss that provides high-impact, velvet matte color without the dry-out. The unique Pro-Sculpt applicator allows you to create endless looks from a bold sculpted look to a nude ombre.

Rimmel's Provocalips 16 Hour Kiss Proof Lip Colour is an exclusive 2 step product that locks in vibrant color for 16 hours. It's so incredibly lightweight and flexible that it adapts to the movement of your lips. These seductively rich shades bring out that femme fatale in you! Wow color, incredible shine and zero trace!

LIPPY is a highly-pigmented, long wearing liquid lipstick designed to complement your favourite Butter London nail lacquers. Butter London's nourishing formula moisturizes and protects with shea butter, and vitamin E. Butter London does not add parabens or phthalates to any of its product formulas. It's colour without compromise.
